vernac_cmds: Lemma MkdirPSS : forall (s t : SFSstate) (u : SUBJECT), FuncPre1 s -> FuncPre2 s -> FuncPre3 s -> SecureState s -> TransFunc u s Mkdir t -> SecureState t.
intros s t Sub FP1 FP2 FP3 SS TF; inversion TF.

cut (match fsecmat (secmat s) o with | Some y => set_In u0 (ActReaders y) -> PreDACRead s u0 o | None => True end /\ match fsecmat (secmat s) o with | Some y => set_In u0 (ActWriters y) -> PreDACWrite s u0 o | None => True end).
unfold PreDACRead, PreDACWrite, mkdir_acl in |- *; simpl in |- *.
elim (fsecmat (secmat s) (MyDir p)); elim (fSSC (subjectSC s) Sub).

replace (facl (set_add ACLeq_dec (NEWDIR p, acldata Sub (primaryGrp s Sub) (ChangeUserR Sub (empty_set SUBJECT) (ownerp perms)) (ChangeGroupR (AllGrp s) (groupp perms) (ChangeGroupR (primaryGrp s Sub) (groupp perms) (empty_set GRPNAME))) (ChangeUserW Sub (empty_set SUBJECT) (ownerp perms)) (ChangeGroupW (AllGrp s) (groupp perms) (ChangeGroupW (primaryGrp s Sub) (groupp perms) (empty_set GRPNAME))) (Sub :: nil) (RootGrp s :: nil)) (acl s)) o) with (facl (acl s) o).
unfold MACSecureState in |- *; simpl in |- *; intros.
elim (fSSC (subjectSC s) u0); elim (fOSC (mkdir_oSC s Sub (ObjName o)) o); contradiction || auto.
replace (DOM OBJeq_dec (objectSC s)) with (DOM OBJeq_dec (acl s)).
rewrite y in H4; rewrite y in H2; eauto.
symmetry in |- *; unfold fsecmat in |- *; apply NotInDOMIsUndef.
rewrite y in H4; rewrite y in H2; eauto.
replace (fOSC (mkdir_oSC s Sub p) o) with (fOSC (objectSC s) o).
unfold MACSecureState in MAC; apply MAC.
Lemma MkdirPSP : forall (s t : SFSstate) (u : SUBJECT), FuncPre1 s -> FuncPre2 s -> FuncPre3 s -> StarProperty s -> TransFunc u s Mkdir t -> StarProperty t.
intros s t Sub FP1 FP2 FP3 SP TF; inversion TF.
unfold StarProperty in |- *; simpl in |- *; intros u0 o1 o2.
elim (OBJNAMEeq_dec p (ObjName o1)); elim (OBJNAMEeq_dec p (ObjName o2)).
elim (fsecmat (secmat s) o2); elim (fOSC (mkdir_oSC s Sub p) o2); elim (fOSC (mkdir_oSC s Sub p) o1); trivial.
elim (fsecmat (secmat s) o2); elim (fOSC (mkdir_oSC s Sub p) o2); elim (fOSC (mkdir_oSC s Sub p) o1); trivial.
elim (fsecmat (secmat s) o1); elim (fOSC (mkdir_oSC s Sub p) o2); elim (fOSC (mkdir_oSC s Sub p) o1); trivial.
replace (fOSC (mkdir_oSC s Sub p) o1) with (fOSC (objectSC s) o1).
replace (fOSC (mkdir_oSC s Sub p) o2) with (fOSC (objectSC s) o2).
unfold StarProperty in SP; apply SP.
Lemma MkdirPCP : forall s t : SFSstate, FuncPre1 s -> FuncPre2 s -> PreservesControlProp s Mkdir t.
intros s t FP1 FP2; unfold PreservesControlProp in |- *; intros Sub TF; inversion TF; unfold ControlProperty in |- *.
rewrite a in H4; rewrite a in H2; eauto.
rewrite H12 in H11; inversion H11; auto.
cut (facl (acl s) o = facl (mkdir_acl s Sub p perms) o).
intro EQ; rewrite <- EQ in H10; rewrite H10 in H9; injection H9; auto.
rewrite a in H4; rewrite a in H2; eauto.
rewrite H12 in H11; inversion H11; auto.
cut (facl (acl s) o = facl (mkdir_acl s Sub p perms) o).
intro EQ; rewrite <- EQ in H10; rewrite H10 in H9; injection H9; auto.
rewrite H12 in H9; discriminate H9.
replace (DOM OBJeq_dec (objectSC s)) with (DOM OBJeq_dec (acl s)).
rewrite a in H4; rewrite a in H2; eauto.
rewrite H12 in H11; inversion H11; auto.
cut (fOSC (objectSC s) o = fOSC (mkdir_oSC s Sub p) o).
intro EQ; rewrite <- EQ in H10; rewrite H10 in H9; injection H9; auto.
